+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[gL], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subscript[g, SubscriptStyle[Format[L, NiceForm]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[gs], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subscript[g, SubscriptStyle[Format[s, NiceForm]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[gY], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subscript[g, SubscriptStyle[Format[Y, NiceForm]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[Yu, ind_], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subsuperscript[Y, SubscriptStyle[Format[u, NiceForm]], 
+       SubscriptStyle[Row[(Format[#1, NiceForm] & ) /@ ind]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[Yd, ind_], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subsuperscript[Y, SubscriptStyle[Format[d, NiceForm]], 
+       SubscriptStyle[Row[(Format[#1, NiceForm] & ) /@ ind]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[Ye, ind_], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subsuperscript[Y, SubscriptStyle[Format[e, NiceForm]], 
+       SubscriptStyle[Row[(Format[#1, NiceForm] & ) /@ ind]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[label_, ind_], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subsuperscript[C, SubscriptStyle[
+        Format[Symbol[StringReplace[ToString[label], "C" -> ""]], NiceForm]], 
+       SubscriptStyle[Row[(Format[#1, NiceForm] & ) /@ ind]]], NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[label:\[Mu] | \[Lambda]], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[label, NiceForm]
+ 
+Coupling /: MakeBoxes[Coupling[label_], NiceForm] := 
+     Format[Subscript[C, SubscriptStyle[Format[label, NiceForm]]], NiceForm]
+
